So this is letting Digicert know its ok to switch over to using the
SHA-2 signed signing cert for signing new cert requests. In theory,
should be transparent, but it would probably be best to pick a date in
the future and let everyone know, just in case someone happens to have
1000 host certs expiring the day after and it turns out there is a
problem...

-kevin

